title: slapd syncrepl status
agents: linux
catalog: app/slapd
license: GPL
distribution: Markus Weber
description:
 This check monitors the status of the sync replication of a slapd consumer.
 It can also monitor Multi-Master replication.

item:
 SLAPD {{Instance name}} syncrepl status

perfdata:
 None

inventory:
 One service will be created for each slapd instance configured in local config file.
